    stable 1.1.14 1.1.10 1.1.8 1.1.3
   require glut gtk+
  category game
 attribute new x11
    source http://savannah.nongnu.org/download/crack-attack/crack-attack-$VERSION.tar.bz2
  homepage http://www.nongnu.org/crack-attack/
  estimate 100
      desc 'crack-attack is a network multi-player variation of tetris.
crack-attack is a puzzle/action game in which you rush
to eliminate colored blocks before they fill your screen.'

